         "HologramLib":{
            "enabled":true,
            "route":"/projects/hologramlib",
            "navbar":false,
            "title":"HologramLib",
            "meta_title": "HologramLib",
            "meta_description": "Minecraft hologram library with text, item & block displays, leaderboards, and extensive customization. packet-based, modern & easy to use", 
            "description":"A powerful **<gradient>packet-based</gradient>** text display hologram library for Minecraft servers with MiniMessage support, emoji rendering, and extensive customization options.",
            "images":[
               "/images/projects/pages/hologramlib/1.png",
               "/images/projects/pages/hologramlib/2.png",
               "/images/projects/pages/hologramlib/3.png"
            ],
            "content":[
                  {
                     "type":"text",
                     "content":"**HologramLib** is a display entity-based hologram library for modern Minecraft servers (**1.19.4** to **1.21.5**).<br>It allows developers to create dynamic, customizable holograms using packets, with support for MiniMessage formatting, animations, and per-player visibility.<br><br>It works with Paper, Purpur, Spigot, and Folia servers, and requires PacketEvents as a dependency.<br>It __does not__ support **Bedrock** or older Minecraft versions (~~1.8 to 1.19.3~~).<br><br><white>**The library supports multiple hologram types:**</white><br> · Text with styling, scaling, background colors<br> · Blocks and Items displayed as holograms<br> · Leaderboards with live updates<br><br><white>**Advanced features include:**</white><br> · Animation support<br> · Entity attachment (e.g. hologram on a mob)<br> · View distance control<br> · Per-player visibility and interactivity (planned)<br><br>Integration is simple with a [JitPack](https://jitpack.io/#HologramLib/HologramLib) dependency and a few lines of code. Full usage examples are provided in the [Wiki](https://github.com/maximjsx/HologramLib/wiki)"
                  },
                  {
                     "type":"features",
                     "title":"Key Features",
                     "items":[
                        "Packet-based",
                        "MiniMessage support",
                        "Custom emoji and Unicode character support",
                        "Multi-line",
                        "Per-player visibility",
                        "Easy to use API",
                        "Animations",
                        "Text, blocks, items, and leaderboards",
                        "Entity attachment"
                     ]
                  },
                  {
                     "type":"text",
                     "content":"<white>**__Contributors__</white>**<br>[maximjsx](https://github.com/maximjsx), [misieur](https://github.com/misieur), [WhyZerVellasskx](https://github.com/WhyZerVellasskx), [RootException](https://github.com/RootException) &  [matt11matthew](https://github.com/matt11matthew)"
                  }
               ],
